       <div class="desc"> 
        <h3><a id="cphContent_cphMain_ucStorySnippet_hlkStoryLink" href="/stories/story.aspx?story_id=180"><span itemprop="name">Overcoming military sexual trauma</span></a></h3> 
        <p itemprop="description">Veterans who experienced military sexual trauma share their stories. They describe the challenges they faced and how their lives were affected. Eventually, these men and women reached out for support. Hear how they were able to get on the road to recovery.</p> 
        <div class="snippet-links"> 
         <a id="cphContent_cphMain_ucStorySnippet_hlkWatchNow" class="more" href="/stories/story.aspx?story_id=180">Watch Now</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;
